gnd completions — print a shell completion script for gnd.

Usage:  gnd completions <bash|zsh|fish>

The generated scripts complete subcommands and complete declared IDs for
`gnd show <ID>` and `gnd refs <ID>` by calling the hidden helper:
`gnd complete ids --prefix <word>`.

Install examples:
  source <(gnd completions bash)
  gnd completions zsh > ~/.zfunc/_gnd
  gnd completions fish > ~/.config/fish/completions/gnd.fish

Exit:  0 script printed · 2 unsupported shell.
